# circumsphere

- _circumsphere(t)_

Answer the circumsphere,
or circumscribed sphere,
of the `Tetrahedron` _t_.

```
>>> Tetrahedron([0 0 0; 1 0 0; 0 1 0; 0 0 1])
>>> .circumsphere
Sphere([1/2 1/2 1/2], 1/3.pi.sin)
```

